SUMMARY:3rd Friday Boardgame Night
DESCRIPTION:Central PA Game Club\nEvery 3rd Friday of the month we gather 
 to play boardgames at East Shore Baptist Church. Join us!\n\n**Where:**\nE
 ast Shore Baptist Church\n6721 Jonestown Rd.\nHarrisburg\, PA 17112\n\n**W
 hen:**\n3rd Friday of the month at 6:30pm\n\n**What Games?**\nAny and all!
