SUMMARY:Carlisle’s Monday Game Night
DESCRIPTION:Central PA Game Club\nCarlisle’s Monday Game Night.\nMost at
 tendees are playing modern designer games like Ticket to Ride\, Catan\, Ca
 rcassonne\, Wingspan\, etc. Guests are always welcome to bring classic gam
 es (Scrabble\, Backgammon\, playing cards).\n\n* All ages are welcome.\n\n
 * Completely free to attend.\n\n* Learn a game\, bring a game\, teach a ga
 me.\n\n* There will always be a few games acailable to play.\n\n* Feel fre
 e to bring your own!\n\n• While we do ask that you RSVP\, many people fo
 rget to RSVP. So while the attendance list may look like no one is attendi
 ng\, people still show up.\n\n* You do not need to show up exactly at the 
 start time. Feel free to drop in at any time.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/centralpagameclub/events/313623937/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260303T223947Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260303T223947Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
