DESCRIPTION:Central PA Game Club\nCome join us at Lazarus Games to meet ot
 hers interested in playing RPGs. Bring your own dice if you have them.\n\n
 Please be sure to join our Discord to select "Attending" so that the GM ca
 n prep for the correct number of attendees! https://discord.gg/Sq5SvqkN\n\
