SUMMARY:Wednesday Game Night - Calvary UMC Dillsburg Family Center
DESCRIPTION:Central PA Game Club\nThe Dillsburg Game Night has been going 
 strong since 2016. We meet every Wednesday from 6:30-9:30pm for casual tab
 letop games.\nWe are a group of about 30-40 gamers who love to learn and t
 each new games. You won’t find a more welcoming group… it’s not that
  we’re desperate for you to come back or anything like that 😉. But in
  all seriousness\, it’s a great group of friendly people.\nGiven the tim
 eframe we typically just do light to medium weight Euros. We have 200+ boa
 rd games available to play and people typically bring games.\nWe run long 
 game days every other month (usually a Saturday 2pm-9pm). We do Magic the 
 Gathering on the first Wednesday of ever month (in addition to boardgames)
 . We do monthly themed nights. Check out our Facebook for additional event
 s.\nCost: Free\nWho: All ages (under 15 must be accompanied by an adult)\n
 When: Every Wednesday (6:30pm-9:30pm)\nWhere: Calvary UMC of Dillsburg\, i
 n the Family Center\nFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/groups/22493453351
 00181\nThanks!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/centralpagameclub/events/310622317/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20250820T233117Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20250820T233117Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
